docs {
  ## cuid demo — step 2

  Retrieve all BusinessPartners.

  Every record has an `ID` field — a UUID generated by CAP
  on INSERT. We never supplied it. Add a few more via step 1
  and run this again to see each gets a unique UUID.
}
